WEBVTT

00:00.267 --> 00:01.986
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:02.027 --> 00:04.261
He took me out to the church's camp.

00:04.296 --> 00:07.430
He said he was just going
to teach me how to fish.

00:07.466 --> 00:09.299
You need to stay out of my way.

00:09.334 --> 00:11.234
- I mean it.
- Get out of my office now.

00:11.270 --> 00:13.202
You start pulling threads
to get to me, girl,

00:13.237 --> 00:14.570
you're going to unravel the whole thing.

00:14.605 --> 00:16.938
What exactly did the auditor say?

00:16.974 --> 00:19.107
She wants our personal income taxes,

00:19.143 --> 00:21.177
complete with receipts,
for the last three years.

00:21.212 --> 00:22.611
When were you going to tell me?

00:22.647 --> 00:24.246
After they put me in prison?

00:24.282 --> 00:25.658
I should go.

00:26.667 --> 00:28.584
Sometimes I wonder if he isn't still

00:28.619 --> 00:30.017
holding a torch for Grace.

00:30.053 --> 00:32.520
Well, pardon my lapse
of loyalty, but no.

00:33.237 --> 00:35.456
After a thorough investigation

00:35.492 --> 00:37.925
into the fatal shooting of
16-year-old Kenneth Collins,

00:38.249 --> 00:41.562
the grand jury has declined
to bring criminal charges...

00:41.598 --> 00:43.531
- Like I said.
- This is a surprise.

00:43.567 --> 00:45.900
I thought you'd be halfway
to Delaware by now.

00:45.935 --> 00:46.866
Yeah, well, you got me thinking.

00:47.398 --> 00:50.042
For my brother.

00:50.072 --> 00:51.305
Oh, my God!

